OL,3,CHospital boss 'constructively
OL,4,Cdismissed' as tribunal slams NHS chiefs
OL,6,FA former hospital CEO was
OL,7,Fconstructively dismissed with
OL,8,Fmanagement reportedly purging
OL,9,F"hundreds of messages and documents"
OL,10,Fin an alleged bid to evade
OL,11,Faccountability.
OL,13,FDr Susan Gilby, who worked for the
OL,14,FCountess of Chester Hospital, endured
OL,15,Fconstructive dismissal following her
OL,16,Fwhistleblowing activities, an
OL,17,Femployment tribunal has ruled.
