OL,3,CHospital boss 'constructively
OL,4,Cdismissed' as tribunal slams NHS chiefs
OL,6,FThe British Medical Association (BMA),
OL,7,Fwhich advocates for doctors across the
OL,8,FUK, branded the "distressing torment"
OL,9,FDr Gilby experienced at the hands of
OL,10,Fthe trust as "nothing short of
OL,11,Fdisgraceful".
OL,13,FFurther findings revealed that
OL,14,FCountess of Chester management had
OL,15,Finitiated a dubious operation,
OL,16,Freferred to as 'Project Countess',
OL,17,Fwhere they reportedly purged "hundreds
OL,18,Fof messages and documents" in an
OL,19,Falleged bid to evade accountability.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
