OL,3,CHospital boss 'constructively
OL,4,Cdismissed' as tribunal slams NHS chiefs
OL,6,FDr Gilby lodged a formal whistle-
OL,7,Fblowing complaint in July 2022 against
OL,8,Fthe chairman, voicing her concerns
OL,9,Fabout his conduct to both the NHS
OL,10,Ftrust and NHS England.
OL,12,FIn response to her allegations, Dr
OL,13,FGilby stated the trust offered her a
OL,14,Fsecondment to a high-level advisory
OL,15,Fposition within NHS England on the
OL,16,Fprovision that she recant her
OL,17,Faccusations.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
