OL,3,CHospital boss 'constructively
OL,4,Cdismissed' as tribunal slams NHS chiefs
OL,6,FSubsequently, NHS England approached
OL,7,Fher regarding a role. Dr Gilby,
OL,8,Fhowever, in November, declined to
OL,9,Fretract her claims; the trust
OL,10,Fsuspended her on 2 December.
OL,12,FFollowing this, on 5 December, she
OL,13,Fnotified the trust of her decision to
OL,14,Fresign after a six-month notice period.
OL,16,FProfessor Philip Banfield, BMA council
OL,17,Fchair, has responded to the employment
OL,18,Ftribunal's findings by condemning the
OL,19,Fhospital management's actions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
