OL,3,CHospital boss 'constructively
OL,4,Cdismissed' as tribunal slams NHS chiefs
OL,6,F"When doctors raise concerns, they
OL,7,Fshould be listened to and handled
OL,8,Ffairly, with a mind to understanding
OL,9,Fthe situation, what may be going wrong
OL,10,Fand what needs to done to fix things,"
OL,11,Fhe said.
OL,13,F"Instead, Dr Gilby faced a deliberate
OL,14,Fand concerted effort to force her out
OL,15,Fin response to her whistleblowing."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
