OL,6,FIn addition to this, he exposed that
OL,7,F"Following this already appalling
OL,8,Fbehaviour, management at the Countess
OL,9,Fof Chester embarked on a cover-up
OL,10,Fknown as 'Project Countess', deleting
OL,11,Fhundreds of messages and documents in
OL,12,Fan attempt to escape accountability
OL,13,Ffor their actions."
OL,15,FProfessor Banfield expressed his
OL,16,Fdisapproval, saying: "It was
OL,17,Funacceptable in Chester, and it is
OL,18,Funacceptable anywhere.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
