OL,3,CHospital boss 'constructively
OL,4,Cdismissed' as tribunal slams NHS chiefs
OL,6,F"We were glad to support Dr Gilby in
OL,7,Fher case, and sincerely hope that this
OL,8,Fruling means she can begin to recover
OL,9,Ffrom this terrible ordeal."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
