OL,3,CHospital boss 'constructively
OL,4,Cdismissed' as tribunal slams NHS chiefs
OL,6,FFurthermore, the BMA council chair
OL,7,Fhighlighted that: "While shocking,
OL,8,Fthis incident is sadly not an isolated
OL,9,Fone. The ongoing treatment of those
OL,10,Fraising patient safety concerns to
OL,11,Fresponsible bodies or regulators
OL,12,Fremains appalling and too readily
OL,13,Fdismissive; the protections afforded
OL,14,Fare inadequate and the legislation in
OL,15,Fthis area remains not fit for purpose.
OL,16,FThe culture of fear and blame across
OL,17,Fthe NHS remains endemic.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
