OL,3,CHospital boss 'constructively
OL,4,Cdismissed' as tribunal slams NHS chiefs
OL,6,F"We will continue to fight for doctors
OL,7,Fwho find themselves in this terrible
OL,8,Fposition, and continue our campaigns
OL,9,Ffor regulation of NHS managers.
OL,11,F"More than anything, we need a radical
OL,12,Fshakeup of patient safety in
OL,13,Fhealthcare. It's time we see an end to
OL,14,Fthese dangerously casual attitudes and
OL,15,Fthe woeful under-resourcing of patient
OL,16,Fsafety interventions."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
